title: UXL Encyclopedia of World Mythology - 1st Ed (5 Vol Set) Gooner
description:
Publisher: UXL; 1 edition (September 23, 2008)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1414430302
ISBN-13: 978-1414430300

This five-volume set brings clarity out of confusion for the middle and high school student studying world mythology. The 300 A-to-Z entries from 40-plus cultures are grouped into five categories (character, deity, myth, theme, and culture) and come with a reader's guide that explores major themes in world mythology
